{"tid":1256511,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【水緊，又cap水】財政部下周首度於澳門發行人民幣國債　規模達20億元","createTime":"2019-06-25T05:19:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T09:46:14.000Z","uid":54337,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"502fb13e5af87a20a366f210edbd0ea9b3d9155d","tid":1256511,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T05:19:10.000Z","msg":"財政部下周首度於澳門發行人民幣國債 規模達20億元<br />\n<br />\n中國財政部宣布，將於下周四（7月4日）於澳門首度發行20億元人民幣國債，以支持澳門發展特色金融，並鼓勵更多發行體於當地發行人民幣債券。渣打認為，此次發行意味澳門將成為香港以外，另一人民幣國債的離岸發行地，但對本港影響有限。<br />\n<br />\n冀加快推動澳門債市發展<br />\n<br />\n財政部於網站公告，中央政府在澳門發行人民幣國債，有助支持澳門發展特色金融、促進澳門經濟適度多元可持續發展，亦為澳門人民幣市場發展的里程碑，對於引導更多發行體在澳門發行人民幣債券、加快推動澳門債券市場建設具有重要意義。財政部認為，發行人民幣國債將加強內地與澳門的金融合作，並為投資者提供安全穩健的投資選擇。<br />\n<br />\n渣打中國宏觀策略部主管劉潔評論指，人行類似發行可能陸續有來，為中央增添在香港以外的離岸債發行地選擇，但相信在可見將來，其發行規模及頻繁程度仍將較小。此外，由於澳門債券二手市場流動性較香港低，此批國債的利率定價或會略高於以往。<br />\n<br />\n她預料，是次發行對香港市場的影響不大，但隨着澳門加快推動債券市場發展，或會於數年後為香港帶來競爭，尤其是在離岸人民幣債券領域。惟截至4月為止，澳門的離岸人民幣存款為390億元人民幣，僅為香港的6%。"},{"pid":"6d8c9bf94dd1b4503fcfbaea88fd1cfe02d268af","tid":1256511,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T05:19:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/344549/%E8%B2%A1%E6%94%BF%E9%83%A8%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8%E9%A6%96%E5%BA%A6%E6%96%BC%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80%E7%99%BC%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%B9%A3%E5%9C%8B%E5%82%B5-%E8%A6%8F%E6%A8%A1%E9%81%9420%E5%84%84%E5%85%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%25B6%2593%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E8%25A8%258A%2F344549%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E6%2594%25BF%25E9%2583%25A8%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%2591%25A8%25E9%25A6%2596%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E6%2596%25BC%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E9%2596%2580%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%25A1%258C%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25B9%25A3%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2582%25B5-%25E8%25A6%258F%25E6%25A8%25A1%25E9%2581%259420%25E5%2584%2584%25E5%2585%2583&d=DgFN9ivcdgICzBQxXV443qooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=f03b85ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/344549/%E8%B2%A1%E6%94%BF%E9%83%A8%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8%E9%A6%96%E5%BA%A6%E6%96%BC%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80%E7%99%BC%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%B9%A3%E5%9C%8B%E5%82%B5-%E8%A6%8F%E6%A8%A1%E9%81%9420%E5%84%84%E5%85%83</a>"},{"pid":"4547a60d162308bf9bce1ff4c8a7a37f460b55b4","tid":1256511,"uid":1654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T05:23:16.000Z","msg":"20億 就夠？"},{"pid":"b7160b91270e19ea97895e6e1dcf8744bfdcec7b","tid":1256511,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T05:23:44.000Z","msg":"樂觀sir又中"},{"pid":"d2a24060fc95430f67ec4bc0d0fc3601c740c342","tid":1256511,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T05:25:59.000Z","msg":"Cap水？收賭場保護費only<br />\n廿億都唔夠打貿易戰<br />\n明日大罪咁，一萬億就差唔多"},{"pid":"d81449f09e2f988d5fa2d63bfe564d481008845f","tid":1256511,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T05:26:34.000Z","msg":"陰屍紙"},{"pid":"4e16129abcd69f53ba2f690b041e9b6ec6cf1588","tid":1256511,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T06:18:11.000Z","msg":"20億買賣賭仔身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6df87f791c838e82579b3d0501553c95df72c9cc","tid":1256511,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T07:23:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nCap水救銀行？"},{"pid":"da9ff0c2050532ac7973104e944b5c5f4681e448","tid":1256511,"uid":207894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T09:02:19.000Z","msg":"人民幣都夠膽要<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72bdea8b7c92bc3e385071829298908389a6dd33","tid":1256511,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T0